<h4><font size=+2>The Informed Investor - Free Registration!</font><hr></h4>
<font size=+2>T</font>here are many special benefits available to registered users of The Informed Investor web site, including full access to The Informed Investor Newsletter (normal subscription $89.00). It takes just a couple of minutes and, best of all, it's <b>free</b> and without obligation! All we need is some information about you and your investment habits. If you use Netscape, you're welcome to use our <b><a href="https://www.islandnet.com/~cwebster/investor/sregister.html">secure commerce server</a></b> for sending this information.

