<html><head><title>The Informed Investor Newsletter - Mutual Fund News</title></head><body background="../images/tile.gif" bgcolor=#ffffff link=#297b63 vlink=#297b63 alink=#31ad84><a href="../index.html"><img src="../images/home.gif" width=55 height=16 align=right border=0 alt="Home" vspace=5 hspace=5></a>&nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp &nbsp <img src="../titles/mutual.gif"><p><table border=0 cellspacing=0 cellpadding=6><tr><td><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width=95 height=2></td><td><font size=-1 face=Arial><img src="../letters/l.gif" align=left vspace=1 hspace=1>ondon Life Insurance just bought the Prudential line of funds from Prudential Insurance.<p>About $560 million in fund assets is involved.<p>Prudential has gained a fine performance reputation over the last few years, attributed to the recently departed Monika Hirsch. Since Ms. Hirsch's departure, the Pru. have managed to maintain very strong performances, suggesting good depth of portfolio management.<p>BPI Capital has announced an expansion of their portfolio management team with the addition of Kevin Klassen from Crown Life. Mr. Klassen managed Crown Life's Canadian Equity Fund and has considerable venture capital and corporate finance experience. He will be responsible for the $210 million BPI Global Balanced RSP Fund. </td><td> &nbsp</td><td background="../images/tbltile.gif" bgcolor=#c6d6c6 valign=top><center><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width=95 height=2><br><img src="../images/charts.gif" width=80 height=15><font face="Arial" size=-1><hr noshade color=#297b63></center>There are no<br>charts related<br>to this article.</font><p></td></tr></table><p><p><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width=95 height=2 align=left><hr noshade color=#297b63><table border=0 width=100%><tr><td align=center><img src="../images/spacer.gif" width=95 height=2 align=left><a href="canada.html"><img src="../images/back.gif" width=55 height=16 border=0 align=left></a><a href="bonds.html"><img src="../images/next.gif" widt