</STRONG>
</PRE> 
**Countries which are members of OECD but do not have nuclear power or active waste management
programs include Australia, Austria, Denmark, Greece, Iceland, Ireland, Luxembourg, New Zealand,
Norway, Portugal, and Turkey.<P>

