8/96   Comment on Proposed Policy and Procedures for implementing Section 180(c).
<HR> 
<B>Activities for current budget period:</B>
<P>
1.  Conduct annual meeting of the High-Level Radioactive Waste Committee.
<P>
2.  Provide regional spent fuel and high level radioactive waste transportation information.
<P>
3.  Monitor DOE's Section 180(c), NWPA assistance development effort.
<P>
4.  Monitor topics related to NWPA shipment routing.
<P>
5.  Maintain awareness of developments regarding inspection/enforcement procedures for
    commercial vehicles transporting spent nuclear fuel or high-level waste. 
<P>
6.  Work on comprehensive transportation planning for NWPA shipments.
<P>
7.  Maintain awareness of developments in authorizing and constructing an interim storage
    facility.
<P>
8.  Maintain awareness of developments in the Waste Isolation Pilot Plant program.
